PN,36902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1779822664
OL,3,CFamily take on French mountain for boy
OL,4,Cwith rare genetic disorder
OL,6,FIn order to raise funds to help with
OL,7,Fequipment and therapies, John
OL,8,FMcDonnell, a social worker who lives
OL,9,Fin Clowne in North Derbyshire, is
OL,10,Fcycling up Mont Ventoux in France.
OL,12,FJohn is a former colleague of Oscar's
OL,13,Fmum, Kayleigh Steel. He will be joined
OL,14,Fby his siblings Paul and Rebecca, as
OL,15,Fwell as his nephew Josh.
OL,17,FThe mountain is a regular Tour de
OL,18,FFrance stage, with a height of 1,910
OL,19,Fmetres.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1779822664
OL,3,CFamily take on French mountain for boy
OL,4,Cwith rare genetic disorder
OL,6,FJohn said: "I wanted to do what I can
OL,7,Fto help Oscar. He is such a great kid,
OL,8,Fso resilient and keen to not let
OL,9,Fanything stand in his way, in spite of
OL,10,Fhis challenges.
OL,12,F"This is a mountain climb for me but
OL,13,Fthat's just one day. Oscar has to
OL,14,Fsurmount his own mountains every
OL,15,Fsingle day.
OL,17,F"It's going to be quite a challenge -
OL,18,Fa couple of weeks ago the weather was
OL,19,Flooking quite cool, but it's suddenly
OL,20,Fgot a lot hotter!"
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1779822664
OL,3,CFamily take on French mountain for boy
OL,4,Cwith rare genetic disorder
OL,6,FOscar's mum Kayleigh said: "Oscar is a
OL,7,Flovely, smiley and happy little boy
OL,8,Fdespite his devastating condition and
OL,9,Ftough start to life.
OL,11,F"He has a feeding tube and various
OL,12,Fother equipment to support his
OL,13,Fbreathing and lung function. He is a
OL,14,Fwheelchair user and can propel his own
OL,15,Fchair.
OL,17,F"Physio is extremely important for him
OL,18,Fto help gain as much independence
OL,19,Fmovement as possible and eventually as
OL,20,Fhe gets bigger we will have to fund
OL,21,Fsignificant house adaptations.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1779822664
OL,3,CFamily take on French mountain for boy
OL,4,Cwith rare genetic disorder
OL,6,F"As Oscar's parents we're determined
OL,7,Fto give him the best quality of life
OL,8,Fpossible. We're so grateful to John
OL,9,Fand his family for taking on this
OL,10,Fchallenge for us. Every penny really
OL,11,Fcounts and can make such a difference
OL,12,Fto Oscar's life."
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/5
